nodes.text: Fleet Supervisor was a position within the Alliance to Restore the Republic overseeing the fleet assets of a sector. Dwin Wisheel served as the Fleet Supervisor for the Rayter sector. In that position, Wisheel took possession of a VR-10 Cuirilla-Rayl Xylines-class spacetug Worthless Fool that a young procurement officer had purchased from Yearo Seville.
